      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pristine example of Bavarian engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, providing the telepathic steering feedback these chassis are renowned for. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its deep luster with zero oxidative wear, while the interior shows no bolster fatigue. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
